          <title>Jazz come up short in shootout with Phoenix, 134-126</title>
          <description><![CDATA[SALT LAKE CITY (ABC4 Sports) - In an incredible display of shooting by both teams, the Utah Jazz could not keep up with the Phoenix Suns in a 134-126 loss Friday night at the Delta Center. Both teams made 22 three-pointers and shot well over 50 percent from the field.]]></description>
